<HEADLINE>
FT  05 NOV 93 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
GOLD shares extended their gains on steady local and foreign buying and the
index ended 72 up at 1,798. Industrials put on 1 at 4,562 and the overall
index rose 32 to 3,978. Kloof gained R3 at R45 and Gencor 65 cents at
R10.45.
