shares. The holding of Mr Cecil Law, Towry's chairman and founder, together
with his family interests, will be reduced from 51.7 per cent to 41.7 per
cent.
For the year ended June 30, Towry Law reported a pre-tax profit of Pounds
2.43m (Pounds 2.07m).
