      The best selling women's scents
 ----------------------------------------------
 1  Chanel No5 Chanel
 2  Tresor L'Oreal
 3  Vanderbilt L'Oreal
 4  Opium YSL/Elf-Sanofi
 5  Anais Anais L'Oreal
